    <!-- Technical Details Section -->
    <div class="technical-details">
    <h3>Technical Details</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            <strong>Precise Location Mapping:</strong> 
            Utilizes Google’s Geocode API to convert addresses into latitude/longitude coordinates for accurate building location. 
            Google’s Solar API then uses image recognition to identify the exact center of the building for precise solar assessment.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Satellite-Based Solar Data Collection:</strong> 
            Employs image recognition to analyze sunlight exposure on rooftops over different times and seasons. 
            Provides optimized recommendations for solar panel placement, focusing on the most well-lit areas for efficiency.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Visual Insights and Savings Reports:</strong> 
            Generates customizable graphs showing savings by payment options, environmental impact, and utility bill comparisons 
            to assist customers in decision-making.
        </li>
        <li>
            <strong>Enhanced Appointment System:</strong> 
            Offers flexible consultation scheduling with automated notifications, streamlining the solar consultation process for 
            an organized user experience.
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>

